餐完全屌打翠華"},{"pid":"b48a3af581489471886c616fae7a63c67e67472b","tid":1002370,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"太興最多問題係少款，晚飯除咗叫餸之外得好少選擇<br />\n上次叫燒味食到嬲，成80蚊斬埋啲垃圾俾我"},{"pid":"c543eb2350d2865b7c196a91da1fc550967372b7","tid":1002370,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"太興叫做食得落肚"},{"pid":"79257d5d4bf18415b2e29f05dfac34764235c276","tid":1002370,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"翠華早餐抵食，食完都慳兩餐"},{"pid":"537932fe11460dd2ece91ef06ae85800b252d61f","tid":1002370,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"翠華屌打<br />\n太興得燒味<br />\n<br />\n翠華早餐/咖哩/海南雞都對得起個價錢"},{"pid":"b206bac1c50de136635c20069918161071d6a34f","tid":1002370,"uid":186375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"太興晚餐得小菜同燒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而翠華晚餐多款又有西餐揀<br />\n但佢d set dinner多數都唔太好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下午茶太興多款d過翠華<br />\n我下午茶食太興多d順便飲凍奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 太興上幾個月出乳鴿promo幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似都係40蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果變做正常menu就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5d357d4af72b51e0aa92a4d577cae3b210e8cd","tid":1002370,"uid":1239,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T18:46:18.000Z","msg":"翠華淨食海南雞飯，同埋佢有個豬軟骨麵 好好食"},{"pid":"267162d255e34eeffa49976e5779771f983f350e","tid":1002370,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5duaOTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5duaO